Crimson Force 

Genre: Sci-Fi
Year: 2005
Country: USA
Runtime: 85 minutes
Director: David Flores  
Cast: Tony Amendola, Taylor Mac Bowyer, David Chokachi, Jeff Fahey  

 
Plot: The crew of the first manned mission to Mars crash land on the surface in search of a clean everlasting power source they believe to be hidden somewhere beneath the ground. However, the crew find themselves in the middle of a civil war between the High Priest of Mars' royal guards and the High Priestess' warriors. The crew is divided with one half deciding to help the High Priest make peace with Earth and the other side with the High Priestess who is secretly plotting to kill her husband and invade Earth.
